      • disabledtestLockWhilePollingAndResume

        public void disabledtestLockWhilePollingAndResume()
        A lock request created while the system if polling, which should prevent further processing until it is removed. Create 1 files and watch it process all of them. Create a lock and wait for the ack. Create a 2nd file, and it will not be processed. Remove the lock; ack is removed and last file is processed.
